snippet.title: CLIP DUNG BEETLE - MINEO GAMES
snippet.description:
We are happy to released the clip of our first video game : Dung Beetle.
In Dung Beetle, you control a beetle that puts all its efforts into bringing home its ball of dung. Let yourself dive into this small world. Discover that from this point of view, every day is a challenge.

Download the game here ►https://gamejolt.com/games/DungBeetle/251581
Twitter ►https://twitter.com/MineoGames
Facebook ►https://www.facebook.com/MineoGames/
Official website ►https://www.mineogames.com/
